            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周三，4月22日，特朗普宣佈無限期延長與伊朗的停火協議，風險資產全線反彈。美股開市前，美股指期貨集體上升，納指100期貨升180點，升幅達0.68%道指30期升0.36%，標普500期貨升0.51%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"185\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oifVS_Hnv4s9p9i8Tl_KvQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTE4NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/e5fab737d7b8e97b75b91e91cc45dcd9\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大宗商品集體反彈，XAU/USD升0.7%報4753美元，白銀升1.74%報78.02美元。原油升超1.7%，倫敦布倫特原油期貨重返100美元大關；WTI原油期貨現報91.25美元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5ce8ccf8-72b4-3fb7-a64a-3b3bad8df2b7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"666\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EVTyCfJnRP1sYxlonOp9hQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTExNTg-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/bc2c6999da5d85cf142b876dc2fa7956\" width=\"552\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元指數下跌0.07%，現報98.32。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow m