            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "「留學香港」刺激私營宿舍需求\t揭3大隱患！｜借鑑海外經驗\t發牌制能治亂象？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4oGPl8blYU5blRmOTtlJeg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/28hse_com_210/92c1abdf61eedc7448b42992781f34b8\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%88%BA%E6%BF%80%E7%A7%81%E7%87%9F%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82-%E6%8F%AD3%E5%A4%A7%E9%9A%B1%E6%82%A3-%E5%80%9F%E9%91%91%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E7%B6%93%E9%A9%97-%E7%99%BC%E7%89%8C%E5%88%B6%E8%83%BD%E6%B2%BB%E4%BA%82%E8%B1%A1-092135870.html",
